Hello there welcome to Three Amigos, don't get distracted by the name cause except for the word three there is nothing related to this repo. This repo idea is to learn or
understand three languages in one go. If you are learning a programming language for the first time I highly suggest not learning this way. This learning process is understanding 
concepts clearly in one language and check same in other two and we cover only basic concepts, not the advanced ones.

Well, let's get started...
